#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn10.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn10.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn10.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Indakavagga "
msgstr "1. With Indaka "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn10.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Piyaṅkarasutta "
msgstr "6. With Piyaṅkara "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn10.6:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā anuruddho sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time Venerable Sāriputta was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn10.6:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā anuruddho rattiyā paccūsasamayaṃ paccuṭṭhāya dhammapadāni bhāsati. "
msgstr "Now at that time Venerable Anuruddha rose at the crack of dawn and recited passages of the teaching. "

msgctxt "sn10.6:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho piyaṅkaramātā yakkhinī puttakaṃ evaṃ tosesi: "
msgstr "Then the native spirit Piyaṅkara’s Mother soothed her little child, saying: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.452, sc2, verse-num-sc826
msgctxt "sn10.6:2.1"
msgid "“Mā saddaṃ kari piyaṅkara, "
msgstr "“Don’t make a sound, Piyaṅkara! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.6:2.2"
msgid "Bhikkhu dhammapadāni bhāsati; "
msgstr "A mendicant recites passages of the teaching. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.6:2.3"
msgid "Api ca dhammapadaṃ vijāniya, "
msgstr "When we understand a passage, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.6:2.4"
msgid "Paṭipajjema hitāya no siyā. "
msgstr "we can practice for our welfare. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3, verse-num-sc827
msgctxt "sn10.6:3.1"
msgid "Pāṇesu ca saṃyamāmase, "
msgstr "Let us keep from harming living creatures, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.6:3.2"
msgid "Sampajānamusā na bhaṇāmase; "
msgstr "and speak no lying words. "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: susīlyamattano → susīlamattano (bj, mr)
msgctxt "sn10.6:3.3"
msgid "Sikkhema susīlyamattano, "
msgstr "We should train ourselves well in ethics, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn10.6:3.4"
msgid "Api muccema pisācayoniyā”ti. "
msgstr "and hopefully we’ll be freed from the goblin realm.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
